First Department,

June, 1939.

(June 2, 1939.) Mildred J. Jamack, Respondent, v. Robert M. Dick, Appellant.

Judgment affirmed, with costs. No opinion. Present — Martin, P. J., O’Malley, Townley, Cohn and Callahan, JJ.; Martin, P. J., and Townley, J., dissent and vote to reverse and dismiss the complaint.
